{
  "stem": "15694.10",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "In those days, traveling was only for the few and the rich.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "One day, I will tell my children that I also have been in Prague.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Anyway, we were only there for an hour or two, and then the train went on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And then the train stopped after three weeks in front of the camp which we later learned was Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "It also had names like Dora or Mittelbau, where the famous V-1 and V-2 weapons were manufactured.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And we thought, oh, something important again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Little did we know that this was a camp where prisoners have been wasted like nothing on earth. 30,000 to 40,000 people died just because of the way they were worked.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I was there for eight days, you know, which, not much to tell.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Yes, another hanging took place because people were captured.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Some people had escaped and were captured-- three people this time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "But instead of front of standing in front of about 10,000, I stood at the very rear of about 20,000, 30,000, I'm not sure.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And I only saw it from the very great distance.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And I didn't see even the faces, but I saw three people hanging.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "That's the only incident because there were three captured after, you know, being, sort of after escaping.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And obviously, it also, it weighs on your mind if you see these things because it hampers your plans for escape.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Anyway, after eight days, we were taken away to another camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By train again, but a very short journey away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And during this journey, some young fellow whom I had seen in Auschwitz talked to me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I was listening half, but the other half was listening for possibly crevices or loose boards, possibly to escape.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
